{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1087,"text":"So whenever I visit a school\nand talk to students,"},{"time":3604,"text":"I always ask them the same thing:"},{"time":6754,"text":"Why do you Google?"},{"time":8624,"text":"Why is Google the search engine\nof choice for you?"},{"time":12855,"text":"Strangely enough, I always get\nthe same three answers."},{"time":15431,"text":"One, \"Because it works,\""},{"time":17494,"text":"which is a great answer;\nthat's why I Google, too."},{"time":20424,"text":"Two, somebody will say,"},{"time":22481,"text":"\"I really don't know of any alternatives.\""},{"time":25708,"text":"It's not an equally great answer\nand my reply to that is usually,"},{"time":28860,"text":"\"Try to Google the word 'search engine,'"},{"time":30805,"text":"you may find a couple\nof interesting alternatives.\""},{"time":33231,"text":"And last but not least, thirdly,"},{"time":35350,"text":"inevitably, one student will raise\nher or his hand and say,"},{"time":38684,"text":"\"With Google, I'm certain to always get\nthe best, unbiased search result.\""},{"time":45157,"text":"Certain to always get the best,\nunbiased search result."}]},{"cues":[{"time":53091,"text":"Now, as a man of the humanities,"},{"time":55505,"text":"albeit a digital humanities man,"},{"time":57710,"text":"that just makes my skin curl,"},{"time":59472,"text":"even if I, too, realize that that trust,\nthat idea of the unbiased search result"},{"time":64382,"text":"is a cornerstone in our collective love\nfor and appreciation of Google."},{"time":68658,"text":"I will show you why that, philosophically,\nis almost an impossibility."}]},{"cues":[{"time":72940,"text":"But let me first elaborate,\njust a little bit, on a basic principle"},{"time":76218,"text":"behind each search query\nthat we sometimes seem to forget."},{"time":79851,"text":"So whenever you set out\nto Google something,"},{"time":81955,"text":"start by asking yourself this:\n\"Am I looking for an isolated fact?\""},{"time":86334,"text":"What is the capital of France?"},{"time":89519,"text":"What are the building blocks\nof a water molecule?"},{"time":91968,"text":"Great -- Google away."},{"time":94333,"text":"There's not a group of scientists\nwho are this close to proving"},{"time":97477,"text":"that it's actually London and H30."},{"time":99498,"text":"You don't see a big conspiracy\namong those things."},{"time":101893,"text":"We agree, on a global scale,"},{"time":103450,"text":"what the answers are\nto these isolated facts."}]},{"cues":[{"time":106199,"text":"But if you complicate your question\njust a little bit and ask something like,"},{"time":111525,"text":"\"Why is there\nan Israeli-Palestine conflict?\""},{"time":114978,"text":"You're not exactly looking\nfor a singular fact anymore,"},{"time":117642,"text":"you're looking for knowledge,"},{"time":119499,"text":"which is something way more\ncomplicated and delicate."},{"time":122600,"text":"And to get to knowledge,"},{"time":124173,"text":"you have to bring 10 or 20\nor 100 facts to the table"},{"time":127228,"text":"and acknowledge them and say,\n\"Yes, these are all true.\""},{"time":130228,"text":"But because of who I am,"},{"time":131926,"text":"young or old, black or white,\ngay or straight,"},{"time":134220,"text":"I will value them differently."},{"time":135855,"text":"And I will say, \"Yes, this is true,"},{"time":137567,"text":"but this is more important\nto me than that.\""},{"time":139705,"text":"And this is where it becomes interesting,"},{"time":141719,"text":"because this is where we become human."},{"time":143889,"text":"This is when we start\nto argue, to form society."},{"time":146909,"text":"And to really get somewhere,\nwe need to filter all our facts here,"},{"time":150290,"text":"through friends and neighbors\nand parents and children"},{"time":152870,"text":"and coworkers and newspapers\nand magazines,"},{"time":154926,"text":"to finally be grounded in real knowledge,"},{"time":158030,"text":"which is something that a search engine\nis a poor help to achieve."}]},{"cues":[{"time":163284,"text":"So, I promised you an example\njust to show you why it's so hard"},{"time":169636,"text":"to get to the point of true, clean,\nobjective knowledge --"},{"time":173064,"text":"as food for thought."},{"time":174556,"text":"I will conduct a couple of simple\nqueries, search queries."},{"time":178473,"text":"We'll start with \"Michelle Obama,\""},{"time":182537,"text":"the First Lady of the United States."},{"time":184365,"text":"And we'll click for pictures."},{"time":187007,"text":"It works really well, as you can see."},{"time":189303,"text":"It's a perfect search\nresult, more or less."},{"time":192355,"text":"It's just her in the picture,\nnot even the President."}]},{"cues":[{"time":195664,"text":"How does this work?"},{"time":197837,"text":"Quite simple."},{"time":199233,"text":"Google uses a lot of smartness\nto achieve this, but quite simply,"},{"time":202472,"text":"they look at two things\nmore than anything."},{"time":204556,"text":"First, what does it say in the caption\nunder the picture on each website?"},{"time":209736,"text":"Does it say \"Michelle Obama\"\nunder the picture?"},{"time":211975,"text":"Pretty good indication\nit's actually her on there."},{"time":214355,"text":"Second, Google looks at the picture file,"},{"time":216765,"text":"the name of the file as such\nuploaded to the website."},{"time":219821,"text":"Again, is it called \"MichelleObama.jpeg\"?"},{"time":222839,"text":"Pretty good indication it's not\nClint Eastwood in the picture."},{"time":225785,"text":"So, you've got those two and you get\na search result like this -- almost."}]},{"cues":[{"time":230074,"text":"Now, in 2009, Michelle Obama\nwas the victim of a racist campaign,"},{"time":236701,"text":"where people set out to insult her\nthrough her search results."},{"time":241430,"text":"There was a picture distributed\nwidely over the Internet"},{"time":244156,"text":"where her face was distorted\nto look like a monkey."},{"time":246824,"text":"And that picture was published all over."},{"time":250017,"text":"And people published it\nvery, very purposefully,"},{"time":253802,"text":"to get it up there in the search results."},{"time":255797,"text":"They made sure to write\n\"Michelle Obama\" in the caption"},{"time":258776,"text":"and they made sure to upload the picture\nas \"MichelleObama.jpeg,\" or the like."},{"time":262977,"text":"You get why -- to manipulate\nthe search result."},{"time":265368,"text":"And it worked, too."},{"time":266687,"text":"So when you picture-Googled\nfor \"Michelle Obama\" in 2009,"},{"time":269431,"text":"that distorted monkey picture\nshowed up among the first results."}]},{"cues":[{"time":272842,"text":"Now, the results are self-cleansing,"},{"time":276432,"text":"and that's sort of the beauty of it,"},{"time":278209,"text":"because Google measures relevance\nevery hour, every day."},{"time":281636,"text":"However, Google didn't settle\nfor that this time,"},{"time":284374,"text":"they just thought, \"That's racist\nand it's a bad search result"},{"time":287522,"text":"and we're going to go back\nand clean that up manually."},{"time":290681,"text":"We are going to write\nsome code and fix it,\""},{"time":293637,"text":"which they did."},{"time":295454,"text":"And I don't think anyone in this room\nthinks that was a bad idea."},{"time":299789,"text":"Me neither."}]},{"cues":[{"time":302802,"text":"But then, a couple of years go by,"},{"time":305858,"text":"and the world's most-Googled Anders,"},{"time":308866,"text":"Anders Behring Breivik,"},{"time":311169,"text":"did what he did."},{"time":312899,"text":"This is July 22 in 2011,"},{"time":314924,"text":"and a terrible day in Norwegian history."},{"time":317597,"text":"This man, a terrorist, blew up\na couple of government buildings"},{"time":321408,"text":"walking distance from where we are\nright now in Oslo, Norway"},{"time":324315,"text":"and then he traveled\nto the island of Ut√∏ya"},{"time":326390,"text":"and shot and killed a group of kids."},{"time":329113,"text":"Almost 80 people died that day."}]},{"cues":[{"time":332397,"text":"And a lot of people would describe\nthis act of terror as two steps,"},{"time":336980,"text":"that he did two things: he blew up\nthe buildings and he shot those kids."},{"time":340415,"text":"It's not true."},{"time":342326,"text":"It was three steps."},{"time":344493,"text":"He blew up those buildings,\nhe shot those kids,"},{"time":346731,"text":"and he sat down and waited\nfor the world to Google him."},{"time":351227,"text":"And he prepared\nall three steps equally well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":354544,"text":"And if there was somebody\nwho immediately understood this,"},{"time":357358,"text":"it was a Swedish web developer,"},{"time":358906,"text":"a search engine optimization expert\nin Stockholm, named Nikke Lindqvist."},{"time":362553,"text":"He's also a very political guy"},{"time":364165,"text":"and he was right out there\nin social media, on his blog and Facebook."},{"time":367465,"text":"And he told everybody,"},{"time":368695,"text":"\"If there's something that\nthis guy wants right now,"},{"time":371174,"text":"it's to control the image of himself."},{"time":374760,"text":"Let's see if we can distort that."},{"time":377490,"text":"Let's see if we, in the civilized world,\ncan protest against what he did"},{"time":381491,"text":"through insulting him\nin his search results.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":384832,"text":"And how?"},{"time":386797,"text":"He told all of his readers the following,"},{"time":388877,"text":"\"Go out there on the Internet,"},{"time":390765,"text":"find pictures of dog poop on sidewalks --"},{"time":394708,"text":"find pictures of dog poop on sidewalks --"},{"time":396906,"text":"publish them in your feeds,\non your websites, on your blogs."},{"time":400400,"text":"Make sure to write the terrorist's\nname in the caption,"},{"time":403345,"text":"make sure to name\nthe picture file \"Breivik.jpeg.\""},{"time":407856,"text":"Let's teach Google that that's\nthe face of the terrorist.\""},{"time":413552,"text":"And it worked."},{"time":415853,"text":"Two years after that campaign\nagainst Michelle Obama,"},{"time":418775,"text":"this manipulation campaign\nagainst Anders Behring Breivik worked."},{"time":422065,"text":"If you picture-Googled for him weeks after\nthe July 22 events from Sweden,"},{"time":426551,"text":"you'd see that picture of dog poop\nhigh up in the search results,"},{"time":430902,"text":"as a little protest."}]},{"cues":[{"time":433425,"text":"Strangely enough, Google\ndidn't intervene this time."},{"time":438494,"text":"They did not step in and manually\nclean those search results up."},{"time":443964,"text":"So the million-dollar question,"},{"time":445704,"text":"is there anything different\nbetween these two happenings here?"},{"time":449096,"text":"Is there anything different between\nwhat happened to Michelle Obama"},{"time":452313,"text":"and what happened\nto Anders Behring Breivik?"},{"time":454402,"text":"Of course not."},{"time":456861,"text":"It's the exact same thing,"},{"time":458356,"text":"yet Google intervened in one case\nand not in the other."}]},{"cues":[{"time":461244,"text":"Why?"},{"time":463283,"text":"Because Michelle Obama\nis an honorable person, that's why,"},{"time":466607,"text":"and Anders Behring Breivik\nis a despicable person."},{"time":470142,"text":"See what happens there?"},{"time":471701,"text":"An evaluation of a person takes place"},{"time":474980,"text":"and there's only one\npower-player in the world"},{"time":478790,"text":"with the authority to say who's who."},{"time":481882,"text":"\"We like you, we dislike you."},{"time":483647,"text":"We believe in you,\nwe don't believe in you."},{"time":485710,"text":"You're right, you're wrong.\nYou're true, you're false."},{"time":488281,"text":"You're Obama, and you're Breivik.\""},{"time":490791,"text":"That's power if I ever saw it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":495206,"text":"So I'm asking you to remember\nthat behind every algorithm"},{"time":498882,"text":"is always a person,"},{"time":500683,"text":"a person with a set of personal beliefs"},{"time":503202,"text":"that no code can ever\ncompletely eradicate."},{"time":505751,"text":"And my message goes\nout not only to Google,"},{"time":508209,"text":"but to all believers in the faith\nof code around the world."},{"time":511043,"text":"You need to identify\nyour own personal bias."},{"time":514043,"text":"You need to understand that you are human"},{"time":516080,"text":"and take responsibility accordingly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":519891,"text":"And I say this because I believe\nwe've reached a point in time"},{"time":522853,"text":"when it's absolutely imperative"},{"time":524432,"text":"that we tie those bonds\ntogether again, tighter:"},{"time":527673,"text":"the humanities and the technology."},{"time":530483,"text":"Tighter than ever."},{"time":532312,"text":"And, if nothing else, to remind us\nthat that wonderfully seductive idea"},{"time":535675,"text":"of the unbiased, clean search result"},{"time":538367,"text":"is, and is likely to remain, a myth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":541984,"text":"Thank you for your time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":543167,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}